role_description: An Ansible role that installs Argo Tunnel Client on nearly any system
role_description_full_overview: [Argo Tunnel Client](https://developers.cloudflare.com/argo-tunnel/) contains the command-line client for Argo Tunnel, a tunneling daemon that proxies any local webserver through the Cloudflare network
role_description_alt: This repository is the home of an Ansible role that installs Argo Tunnel Client on nearly any system.
